{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01SmQVW9utbUjpvhXB39Y31Q","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! Now I have all the information. Let me provide you with a comprehensive summary of the E2E test infrastructure.\n\n## E2E Test Infrastructure Summary\n\nI've read all the key files for your E2E test setup. Here's a complete overview:\n\n### **File Locations (Absolute Paths)**\n\n1. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.local.config.ts`\n2. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.real.config.ts`\n3. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.config.ts`\n4. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/fixtures.ts`\n5. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/smoke.spec.ts`\n6. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/wallets.ts`\n7. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/visual/routes.spec.ts`\n8. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/visual/states.spec.ts`\n9. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/real/startup.spec.ts`\n\n---\n\n### **Test Infrastructure Overview**\n\n#### **Playwright Version & Setup**\n- **Version**: `@playwright/test@^1.58.2`\n- **3 Config Files**: Different modes for different testing purposes\n- **Package.json Scripts**:\n  - `test:visual` - Run visual regression tests (mock mode)\n  - `test:visual:update` - Update visual snapshots\n  - `test:real` - Real wallet mode tests (devnet)\n  - `test:e2e:local` - Local E2E tests (against local validator)\n\n---\n\n### **Three Test Modes**\n\n#### **1. Visual Regression Tests** (`playwright.config.ts`)\n- **Path**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/visual/**/*.spec.ts`\n- **Port**: `3000` (dev server)\n- **Mode**: `VITE_MOCK_MODE: \"true\"`\n- **Features**:\n  - Uses `stablePage` fixture for determinism\n  - Freezes CSS animations, SVG animations, `Date.now()`, `Math.random()`, and `crypto.getRandomValues()`\n  - Seeds PRNG with Mulberry32 algorithm (seed 42)\n  - Frozen date: `2026-01-01T00:00:00Z` (timestamp: 1767225600000)\n  - Snapshot diff tolerance: `maxDiffPixelRatio: 0.015`\n- **Tests Include**:\n  - Route baselines (home, coinflip, crash, profile, etc.)\n  - State variants (wallet disconnected/connected, error toasts)\n\n#### **2. Real Mode Tests** (`playwright.real.config.ts`)\n- **Path**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/real/**/*.spec.ts`\n- **Port**: `3001`\n- **RPC**: `https://api.devnet.solana.com`\n- **Mode**: `VITE_MOCK_MODE: \"false\"`\n- **Features**:\n  - Uses `realPage` fixture (NO randomness freezing)\n  - Collects console errors\n  - Tests real wallet connection flow\n  - Designed for devnet testing\n- **Current Tests**:\n  - App loads without errors in real mode\n  - Wallet icon renders disconnected correctly\n  - Clicking wallet icon calls connect without crashing\n\n#### **3. Local E2E Tests** (`playwright.local.config.ts`)\n- **Path**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/**/*.spec.ts`\n- **Port**: `3002`\n- **RPC**: `http://127.0.0.1:8899` (local validator)\n- **Mode**: `VITE_MOCK_MODE: \"false\"`\n- **Features**:\n  - Single worker, sequential execution\n  - 60 second timeout\n  - Trace retention on failure\n  - Requires external bootstrap (validator + program deploy)\n- **Helper Module**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/wallets.ts`\n\n---\n\n### **Key Fixtures & Helpers**\n\n#### **Shared Visual Fixture** (`e2e/fixtures.ts`)\n```typescript\nexport const test = base.extend<{ stablePage: Page }>({\n  stablePage: async ({ page }, use) => { ... }\n})\n```\n**Capabilities**:\n- Seeded PRNG (Mulberry32, seed 42)\n- Seeded `crypto.getRandomValues()` for deterministic Keypair generation\n- Frozen `Date.now()` → `1767225600000`\n- CSS