ocal |\n|---------|--------|------|-------|\n| Port | 3000 | 3001 | 3002 |\n| Mock Mode | ✓ true | ✗ false | ✗ false |\n| RPC | N/A | devnet | 127.0.0.1:8899 |\n| Parallel | ✓ true | ✓ true | ✗ false (1 worker) |\n| Retries | 0 | 0 | 0 |\n| Fixture Type | stablePage (frozen) | realPage (unfrozen) | Standard page |\n| Console Errors | Assert zero | Assert zero | Assert zero |\n\nThis infrastructure is well-designed for three distinct test scenarios: visual regression (mock), integration (devnet), and local validator testing."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a1c1a59055516fa75 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 40358\ntool_uses: 15\nduration_ms: 41026</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"339d09be-5189-43e7-b291-e94f665f152d","uuid":"f5bd96a9-5cd5-4cf2-ba59-88b584ba9f11","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"I need to understand the existing E2E test infrastructure. Please read:\n1. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.local.config.ts` — the local E2E config\n2. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/smoke.spec.ts` — existing smoke test\n3. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/wallets.ts` — wallet helpers\n4. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.real.config.ts` — real mode config (if exists)\n5. Any other files under `e2e/` directory\n\nAlso check what Playwright version and test utilities are available in package.json.\n\nReturn the full content of each file found.","agentId":"a1c1a59055516fa75","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! Now I have all the information. Let me provide you with a comprehensive summary of the E2E test infrastructure.\n\n## E2E Test Infrastructure Summary\n\nI've read all the key files for your E2E test setup. Here's a complete overview:\n\n### **File Locations (Absolute Paths)**\n\n1. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.local.config.ts`\n2. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/pl